{
  "3215290": {
    "name": "Alien Market Simulator",
    "steam_appid": 3215290,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215290/extras/abcb71227aac0b1c86b9e05a0f8b6150.webp?t=1761302981\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在获得银河警察的保释后，你有机会争取自己的自由。条件是什么？你必须在一个遥远的、未知的星球上管理一座空间站。但这并不是你梦寐以求的自由。你必须每天通过空间站的系统签到，并向当局证明你的价值。只有不断保持任务的进度，你才有希望重新获得独立。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215290/extras/54619004386529222c3ea1e2e859bf82.webp?t=1761302981\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >管理空间站：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>将一个破旧的商店变成繁荣的外星市场。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在修复和升级空间站的同时，经营一个繁忙的星际市场。将其从一个被遗忘的停车站转变为外星旅行者必经的热闹中心，他们在这里寻找零食、燃料以及他们自己都没意识到需要的其他物品。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215290/extras/209c74a0368869b43d35d989f313dc3a.poster.avif?t=1761302981\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215290/extras/209c74a0368869b43d35d989f313dc3a.webm?t=1761302981\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215290/extras/209c74a0368869b43d35d989f313dc3a.mp4?t=1761302981\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215290/extras/2be7219d60c5faf58546d2ddde62e28e.poster.avif?t=1761302981\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215290/extras/2be7219d60c5faf58546d2ddde62e28e.webm?t=1761302981\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215290/extras/2be7219d60c5faf58546d2ddde62e28e.mp4?t=1761302981\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主要特色：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>扫描并销售：</strong> 手动扫描结账商品，完成交易。别忘了给顾客开具收据！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>存货独特物品：</strong> 销售奇异但又熟悉的外星商品——有些合法，有些则……不太合法。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>装饰你的空间站：</strong> 使用AKEA™订购奇特的科幻装饰，改变你的商店氛围。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>管理洗手间：</strong> 外星人也需要上厕所。保持洗手间的清洁，因为开心的膀胱会带来更多的小费。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>雇佣机器人员工：</strong> 自动化清洁、补货和顾客互动。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>订购配送：</strong> 使用机器人快递员从银河目录中补充商品。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>保持清洁：</strong> 脏地板会让顾客生气——保持卫生以保持客流量。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>警惕小偷：</strong> 有些生物会吃掉商品。在它们逃跑之前把它们抓住！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>偿还贷款：</strong> 自由是有代价的。按时还款——否则你准备好迎接来自‘帕达特霍克斯’的惊喜拜访。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >加油站：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为宇宙提供动力！为经过你空间站的银河旅行者提供等离子体、核能和反物质的加油服务。保持他们的飞船平稳运行，发动机保持运转——因为一位加满油的旅行者是一个快乐的旅行者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215290/extras/40f78f7e687c381cd1fe5e22076eed6e.poster.avif?t=1761302981\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215290/extras/40f78f7e687c381cd1fe5e22076eed6e.webm?t=1761302981\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215290/extras/40f78f7e687c381cd1fe5e22076eed6e.mp4?t=1761302981\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为各种外星飞船提供加油服务，满足他们独特的需求。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升级加油技术，实现更快、更安全的服务。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >经营街头餐馆：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快速、奇怪且有点混乱。在不断排队的饥饿顾客中，使用奇异的食材烹饪外星美食。面对奇怪的订单和更奇怪的访客，每一个工作日都像过山车一样刺激。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215290/extras/7c82673f1581a7053c9a6c4525fdaba5.poster.avif?t=1761302981\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215290/extras/7c82673f1581a7053c9a6c4525fdaba5.webm?t=1761302981\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215290/extras/7c82673f1581a7053c9a6c4525fdaba5.mp4?t=1761302981\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主要特色：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>搭建你的摊位：</strong> 安装桌椅和设备，吸引饥饿的外星顾客。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在混乱中烹饪：</strong> 订购奇异的食材，将它们混合成意想不到的菜肴。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>提供服务并赚取收入：</strong> 跟上忙碌的节奏，满足奇怪的口味，赚取那些积分。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >生态系统：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你空间站外的世界是活的！外面是充满奇异生物和外星自然的宁静嗡嗡声。但并非所有的事物都那么友好。有些生物可能变得有点丑陋……可能会把你的顾客吓跑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215290/extras/41985b0159155aa98a0dad637abefd55.poster.avif?t=1761302981\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215290/extras/41985b0159155aa98a0dad637abefd55.webm?t=1761302981\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215290/extras/41985b0159155aa98a0dad637abefd55.mp4?t=1761302981\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>主要特色：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>生动的环境：</strong> 一个根据你的行动和空间站的发展而变化的动态生态系统。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>生物危害区：</strong> 危险的生物质可能在你的空间站附近扩散——清理它或在它变异前将其隔离。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >还有更多内容规划中！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >令人激动的新功能正在开发中——敬请期待！</p>",
